  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dbb \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A group of Kalutara housing officials stole the money of innocent people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the National Housing Development Authority said that several crores of rupees have been defrauded from the loan installments paid for the housing loans taken by low-income earners in Kalutara district.",
        "The official also said that because of that, the work of one clerk and two clerks in that office has already been suspended.",
        "These housing loans have been given to low-income families to build houses and disabled war heroes have also taken the loan money and paid the loan money properly by consuming the loan money obtained, doing rent work, as well as mortgaging the residential land and paying the loan money properly. The officer said that the loan had been properly paid",
        "To know that two parties have been employed to collect the loan given and apart from external persons as debt collection officers, the employees currently working in the Housing Development Authority have also been given the opportunity to do so and arrangements have been made to give them a discount from the money in addition to the monthly salary. have",
        "(When asked about this from Mr. P. A. D. S. Wickramasinghe, the Kalutara District Manager of the National Housing Development Authority, he said the following)",
        "Yes, there has been fraud. As a result of informing the general manager of the head office in writing on the day I came to know about this, an internal investigation is being conducted.",
        "Also, according to a written notice given to the Secretary of the Ministry of Housing and Urban Development, Kalutara, a separate audit will be conducted under his supervision."
      ],
